    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1873-11-23T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1873-11-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="646" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d646">
                <head>No. 644.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Fish</persName> to General <persName type="to">Sickles</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1873-11-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">November</hi> 23,
                                        1873</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Have telegraphed to Borne for authority to Italian minister to take
                                custody of library and property.</p>
                <p>Spanish government, through minister here, proposed arbitration,
                                which has been declined on the ground that the question is not one
                                for arbitration, the subject being one of national honor., of which
                                the nation must be the judge and custodian.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>FISH.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
